### apply agency
POST localhost:8080/api/v1/agencies
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "name": "TOUR.UZ",
  "phone": "998999999999",
  "city": "Tashkent",
  "address": "Yunusobod",
  "email": "eurotouruz@eurotour.uz",
  "description": "tour to europe"
}

### approve agency
POST localhost:8080/api/v1/agencies/approve
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

{
  "agencyId": 2,
  "approve": true
}

### pending agencies
GET localhost:8080/api/v1/agencies/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt}}

### all agencies
GET localhost:8080/api/v1/agencies/all

### update agency
